<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ kāi guǎng wǒ de xīn kāi guǎng wǒ de xīn,
 wǒ jué xīn wǒ jué xīn jué xīn yī kào nǐ,
 wǒ jiù wǎng nǐ mìng lìng de dào shàng zhí bēn.
 nǐ yǒng yuǎn nǐ yǒng yuǎn bù bǎ wǒ diū qì.
 wǒ gǎn xiè wǒ gǎn xiè nǐ de guān huái,
 nǐ yǒng héng bù biàn de ài cháng yǔ wǒ tóng zài.</lyrics>
